1
00:00:48,460 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 4=

3
00:01:06,799 --> 00:01:07,319
Your Highness,

4
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:10,599
let me serve you in the future.

5
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,599
From the moment I met you,

6
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:15,959
everything seems to have been destined.

7
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:17,560
I still remember

8
00:01:18,239 --> 00:01:19,480
when we first met,

9
00:01:20,239 --> 00:01:22,319
you stabbed me
with a commanding presence.

10
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,920
Never speak of

11
00:01:24,239 --> 00:01:25,359
the embarrassing past again.

12
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,200
It was improper.

13
00:01:28,959 --> 00:01:30,200
The improperness

14
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:31,879
brought us here.

15
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:33,560
Am I right?

16
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,000
Ling Xiao,

17
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:39,560
from now on, it's just us.

18
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:42,580
(Yunlai Inn)

19
00:01:47,519 --> 00:01:48,120
Waiter!

20
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:50,640
One bowl of stinky tofu rice noodles!

21
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:51,840
Coming!

22
00:01:56,879 --> 00:01:57,840
Dear customers,

23
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,519
we're about to close for the day.

24
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:01,480
Now we only have one bowl of noodles.

25
00:02:02,159 --> 00:02:04,319
Waiter, I was first, wasn't I?

26
00:02:05,599 --> 00:02:06,159
Well...

27
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:07,680
I ordered it first!

28
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,000
It's mine.

29
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,479
Heard of "first come, first served"?

30
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:14,039
It's my indulging day.

31
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:17,080
I get this bowl of noodles,

32
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:19,479
and you get the money.

33
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,039
Nothing but an upstart.

34
00:02:25,759 --> 00:02:27,680
Seriously? You won't take good money?

35
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:29,800
Miss,

36
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,400
I run a modest business here.

37
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:32,599
For just a bowl of rice noodles,

38
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:35,159
I dare not take so much.

39
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:36,159
See for yourself.

40
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,719
Imperial!

41
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:39,159
Here you go.

42
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,080
Now you have it.

43
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,520
Enjoy!

44
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:43,479
Wait...

45
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:47,639
Fight me for it?
You don't know what's good for you!

46
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:52,759
Smells so good!

47
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,400
You're not getting any!

48
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,560
Go on, lady, enjoy your meal.

49
00:03:03,759 --> 00:03:04,280
You!

50
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,199
A decent woman doesn't fight with a man.

51
00:03:14,439 --> 00:03:15,199
This isn't over.

52
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,479
All bark and no bite.

53
00:03:24,060 --> 00:03:25,620
(Command)

54
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,560
Are you hiding something from me?

55
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:37,520
What do you mean?

56
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,000
That day, actually,

57
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,879
I happened to see
Physician Zhou's medical records.

58
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,039
You...

59
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:45,919
You often suffer from illness,

60
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,199
don't you?

61
00:03:48,319 --> 00:03:49,879
It's just a common cold.

62
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:51,719
There's no need to worry.

63
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,439
Since I have been admitted to
your mansion,

64
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:56,919
I wish to be completely honest with you.

65
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,879
The palace residents are tight-lipped
about your illness.

66
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:02,159
The trials never explicitly mention it,

67
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:03,919
yet they all test whether a man

68
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,680
is willing to give his life for you.

69
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,280
In all of this,

70
00:04:07,639 --> 00:04:08,879
isn't there a connection?

71
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:11,719
I don't want to be a puppet who
knows nothing.

72
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:14,879
This is a matter of my Mu clan.

73
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,879
Outsiders can never interfere.

74
00:04:17,439 --> 00:04:19,040
I'm still just a carpenter's son.

75
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:21,199
Now I stand alone,

76
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,000
but I believe
that human can conquer fate.

77
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:25,399
If you trust me, then tell me.

78
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,040
Some burdens,

79
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,360
when shared by two,

80
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:30,399
are lighter than when borne alone.

81
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:36,319
This is the curse on the royal Mu clan.

82
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:40,000
Only the heart-blood of a beloved one

83
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:42,600
can break the curse.

84
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:49,199
I have so many scars on my body,

85
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,160
and I have bled so much,

86
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,240
I survived it all.

87
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,360
I am willing to offer my heart-blood

88
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:59,199
in exchange for our tomorrow

89
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:01,000
and break the curse on you.

90
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:02,879
If I stay by your side,

91
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:04,399
I can also have

92
00:05:04,759 --> 00:05:07,920
the respect and dignity
I've longed for a lifetime.

93
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:11,319
I don't want you to sacrifice yourself

94
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:14,040
just to fulfill my fate.

95
00:05:15,319 --> 00:05:16,120
We have love.

96
00:05:18,319 --> 00:05:19,759
What is there to fear in sacrifice?

97
00:05:26,519 --> 00:05:27,000
Your Highness!

98
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:27,920
Your Highness!

99
00:05:29,439 --> 00:05:30,120
Your Highness!

100
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,160
Your Highness!

101
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,000
Take the remedy first.

102
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,199
Take the remedy first.

103
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:41,680
Your Highness!

104
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:42,720
Your Highness!

105
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:51,759
Your Highness!

106
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:52,839
Don't scratch!

107
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,000
Don't hurt yourself!

108
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:54,879
Take it out on me instead!

109
00:05:55,199 --> 00:05:55,800
Let me help you!

110
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:08,920
You are good now.

111
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,480
You are good now.

112
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:13,160
(I never expected Ling Xiao)

113
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:16,519
(to be the one who can break my curse.)

114
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,759
(It seems)

115
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,879
(I have truly fallen for him.)

116
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:27,199
(Eight years ago)
I heard your mother was a palace maid.

117
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,920
Though you share the surname of Ling,

118
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,160
you're an unfavored son of a concubine.

119
00:06:31,959 --> 00:06:34,519
No wonder Dongqing sent you
as a hostage prince to Xiling.

120
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:36,600
For generation after generation,

121
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,680
you will always be our slaves.

122
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:41,560
Father will come for me.

123
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,399
Your father?

124
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,480
Our Queen's sword ended him long ago.

125
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,120
This is to repay the blood debt

126
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:48,439
Dongqing owes for
slaughtering our royal family.

127
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:50,519
After that battle,

128
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,319
the world no longer belongs to Dongqing.

129
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,040
People in Dongqing

130
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:55,879
are now Xiling's slaves,

131
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,160
including you,

132
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,279
Ling Xiao.

133
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:04,120
Your Highness.

134
00:07:05,959 --> 00:07:07,240
Recently, we have executed

135
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,279
over 50 hostage princes.

136
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,079
This will be the last one today.

137
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:15,839
Your Highness, here you go.

138
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:17,480
This is Her Majesty's command.

139
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,160
Your Highness,

140
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:52,800
are you alright?

141
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,319
If I mark him as a slave,

142
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,759
will his life be spared?

143
00:08:01,199 --> 00:08:03,560
The centuries-old hatred
between Xiling and Dongqing

144
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,319
cannot be resolved easily.

145
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:08,319
If you defy Her Majesty's command

146
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,160
and show mercy to a hostage prince,

147
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:12,160
he will definitely die.

148
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,160
I hope that one day,

149
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:17,480
this hatred can end with me.

150
00:08:20,519 --> 00:08:21,000
Mother.

151
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,680
I wish to marry Ling Xiao.

152
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:25,680
Say that again?

153
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:28,759
I wish to marry Ling Xiao.

154
00:08:31,879 --> 00:08:33,559
You are Princess of Xiling,

155
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,360
yet you would take a lowborn wretch?

156
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:38,559
Have you no regard
for propriety or decency?

157
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:40,919
This match is completely impossible.

158
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:43,919
I never knew

159
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:46,559
that a lowly slave
harbored such deep schemes.

160
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:47,639
Guards!

161
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,679
Throw him out

162
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,279
and put him to death!

163
00:08:51,639 --> 00:08:52,320
Who dares!

164
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:53,919
I came today

165
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,799
not to negotiate with Your Majesty,

166
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,919
but to inform you

167
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,840
that my mind is made up.

168
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:02,360
Have you forgotten your duty?

169
00:09:02,799 --> 00:09:05,440
You would abandon your grand purpose
for a lowly slave?

170
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,159
For 20 years,

171
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:08,879
I have followed your commands.

172
00:09:09,279 --> 00:09:11,039
I never once stepped out of line.

173
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:11,919
But now,

174
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:14,000
I only want someone I love.

175
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:20,879
You throw everything away
for personal desire,

176
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,240
and you abandon it all.

177
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,799
Eventually,

178
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,480
you will regret this.

179
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:31,360
Even if you don't agree,

180
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:33,879
he

181
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,279
is mine.

182
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:40,559
Your Highness,

183
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:44,600
do you remember the first time we met?

184
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:46,399
It was just like this,

185
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:48,519
you standing before me,

186
00:09:50,919 --> 00:09:52,600
touching my face gently.

187
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,879
Since I met you,

188
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:58,000
every moment is so impressive.

189
00:10:44,399 --> 00:10:45,600
What do you want?

190
00:10:47,519 --> 00:10:48,399
Mu Ruyi.

191
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:50,960
Do you know

192
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,559
how long I've been waiting

193
00:10:54,879 --> 00:10:56,200
for this moment?

194
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,960
Who exactly are you?

195
00:11:01,679 --> 00:11:03,840
I am Prince of Dongqing,

196
00:11:05,679 --> 00:11:06,799
Ling Xiao.

197
00:11:10,799 --> 00:11:12,960
Why did you cure my illness?

198
00:11:13,919 --> 00:11:15,279
Why not just poison me?

199
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,840
I tampered with the tonic

200
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,960
you take every day

201
00:11:19,279 --> 00:11:20,759
to ruin your health.

202
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:23,320
Only by saving you

203
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:25,840
could I earn the chance to kill you.

204
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:29,320
Why were you willing to die for me?

205
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:32,639
I never was.

206
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:36,559
It was nothing but a trick.

207
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:41,879
Even our first encounter

208
00:11:43,039 --> 00:11:43,799
and our falling in love

209
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,679
were all part of your scheme?

210
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:53,240
Now that you know the truth,

211
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:57,759
you can at least have a swift death.

212
00:11:59,559 --> 00:12:00,279
Enough.

213
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:02,399
Your time has come,

214
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:05,360
Your Highness.
